{"about_the_game":"Hi. My friend and I made this game. I hope you like it=)<br>Spirits of the Silicium Forest has several modes: <strong>Story</strong> and <strong>Rogue-lite</strong>.<br>Therefore, the game suits both the players who came for the <strong>aesthetics</strong>, atmosphere and <strong>story</strong>; and those who want to dive very deeply into the gameplay part of the game, <strong>experiment with a ton of different skills</strong>, unique builds and ways of beating the game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233220/extras/story.png?t=1731588803\" /><br>A young girl named <strong>Tzap\u2019lia</strong> has been given a great honor. Her life<strong> will become a gift</strong> to the merciful gods who guard the village from the evil spirits of the <strong>Silicium Forest</strong>.<br>But just as Tzap'lia thought she was getting used to her new role, her mother, a formerly captive priestess of the neighboring village, said that today was the day when <strong>Tzap\u2019lia had to run away</strong>.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233220/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1731588803\" /><br>Aside from the story and aesthetics, the main enjoyment of the game is built on the ability to solve various tactical problems in many different ways.<br>The game encourages an<strong> intellectual and creative approach</strong>.<br>At the same time, gameplay-wise it's <strong>not a clone</strong> of well-known representatives of the genre with minor changes.<br>The turn order, the ability to change position, the build system rather than the deck system, as well as runes, items, summons and other mechanics allowed me to create new and <strong>interesting game situations</strong>. While conceptually preserving the spirit of the genre.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2233220/extras/osobeneng.png?t=1731588803\" /><br><strong>Builds and skills</strong> - more than 200 abilities from which you can form many different playstyles with their own objectives and unique gameplay.<br><strong>Position system</strong> - it's important not only to form your build and use the acquired abilities, but also to tactically move around the battlefield.<br><strong>Rune system</strong> - the correct use of runes allows you to outplay your enemies and get out of even the most dire situations.<br><strong>Story</strong> mode and<strong> rogue-lite</strong> mode - learn the story of Tzap\u2019lia and other heroes as they journey through the Silicium Forest or participate in a randomized run, with a simple and flexible system to customize your adventure.<br><br><strong>Join my Discord channel</strong> , where you can chat with me directly.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginning of the ascent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/0fc641b7f463bdc2be6ba2c8a2d887ed7b77a3e8.jpg"},{"name":"Change your destiny","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/21186646ed0111dc39779818a913928f1176c08c.jpg"},{"name":"The first step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/3e151dbdca5e199e0571490b35f1e6d458cb5206.jpg"},{"name":"Second step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/f8ad0fc2e629ac3cd8bc64844b99f37ef47c2104.jpg"},{"name":"World layers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/a5f94cd6a655e50a5df7c2588dc081ee32818ade.jpg"},{"name":"Third step","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/5a42844db0dc0362b6e1e3f44281dad035417053.jpg"},{"name":"The summit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2233220/e91888bde9a7272634c444c2e1e5f5761c861688.jpg"},{"name":"Time lo